        <div class="num">Our story — Oliver Hudson</div>
        <h2>Built by someone who <em>plays.</em></h2>
        <p>I'm Oliver — an ex-professional tennis player. I spent years searching for a hydration and recovery product that actually worked, and never found one. Sports drinks were mostly sugar. Electrolyte sachets under-dosed the minerals that matter.</p>
        <p>That search led me to <strong>9× fire-roasted bamboo salt</strong> — a 1,000-year-old Korean tradition. We track down the rare highest grade no other electrolyte sachet uses: pH 12, 70+ trace minerals, hydroxyl ions. That's how IONIQ came to life — the hydration, recovery and clean energy I wish I'd had on court.</p>
